### ===========================
### HOME CONTROLLER REQUESTS
### ===========================

### Get Secret from Home Controller
GET {{baseUrl}}/secret
Accept: application/json

### ===========================
### DEMO CONTROLLER REQUESTS
### ===========================

### Submit Demo Command
POST {{baseUrl}}/Demo/SubmitDemoCommand
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Submit Demo Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/Demo/SubmitDemoEvent
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### ===========================
### AUTHENTICATE CONTROLLER REQUESTS
### ===========================

### Authenticate with API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/Authenticate
x-gnx-apikey: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Authenticate with JWT Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/Authenticate
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get User Info (requires JWT with gnx-operator role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/Authenticate/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ===========================
### EXTERNAL API CONTROLLER REQUESTS
### ===========================

### External API Home
GET {{baseUrl}}/ExternalApi
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### External API Post Issue
POST {{baseUrl}}/ExternalApi
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": "12345",
  "description": "Sample issue description",
  "priority": "High"
}

### ===========================
### FIREBASE AUTHORIZED CONTROLLER REQUESTS
### ===========================

### Get Authorized (requires Firebase JWT with Editor role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/FirebaseAuthorized
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get User Info (Firebase Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/FirebaseAuthorized/user-info
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Join Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/FirebaseAuthorized/join-request
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ===========================
### HEALTH AND STATUS ENDPOINTS
### ===========================

### Health Check (if available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Application Info (if available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/info
Accept: application/json

