### ===========================
### TESTING WITH INVALID TOKENS
### ===========================

### Test with Invalid JWT Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/Authenticate/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token
Accept: application/json

### Test with Missing API Key
GET {{baseUrl}}/Authenticate
Accept: application/json

### Test Firebase Endpoint without Authorization
GET {{baseUrl}}/FirebaseAuthorized
Accept: application/json

### ===========================
### TESTING SPECIFIC SCENARIOS
### ===========================

### Test CORS (if needed)
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/Demo/SubmitDemoCommand
Origin: https://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type

### Test with Custom Headers
GET {{baseUrl}}/secret
Accept: application/json
X-Custom-Header: test-value
User-Agent: Demo-HTTP-Client/1.0

